aint_chips_wall" src="http://pre.cloudfront.goodinc.com/posts/thumb_1332443689paint_chips_wall.jpg" /></a></div><h4 class="carousel_title"><div class="list_detail">Lifestyle: </div><a href="/post/7-diy-art-projects-to-cure-your-white-walls">7 DIY Art Projects to Cure Your White Walls</a></h4></div><div class="second-element"><div class="carousel_image"><a href="/post/sponsored-navigating-fashion-and-social-impact-with-erik-joule"><img alt="Thumb_1332370445450erik_clothesrack" src="http://pre.cloudfront.goodinc.com/posts/thumb_1332370445450Erik_clothesrack.jpg" /></a></div><h4 class="carousel_title"><div class="list_detail">Lifestyle: </div><a href="/post/sponsored-navigating-fashion-and-social-impact-with-erik-joule">Sponsored: Navigating Fashion and Social Impact with...</a></h4></div></li><li class="main-carousel"><div class="first-element"><div class="carousel_image"><a href="/post/ethical-style-the-dye-it-yourself-revolution"><img alt="Thumb_1332295121dye-it-yourself-a" src="http://pre.cloudfront.goodinc.com/posts/thumb_1332295121dye-it-yourself-a.jpg" /></a></div><h4 class="carousel_title"><div class="list_detail">Lifestyle: </div><a href="/post/ethical-style-the-dye-it-yourself-revolution">Ethical Style: The Dye-It-Yourself Revolution</a></h4></div><div class="second-element"><div class="carousel_image"><a href="/post/dealbreaker-he-held-me-back"><img alt="Thumb_1332355087db23" src="http://pre.cloudfront.goodinc.com/posts/thumb_1332355087db23.jpg" /></a></div><h4 class="carousel_title"><div class="list_detail">Lifestyle: </div><a href="/post/dealbreaker-he-held-me-back">Dealbreaker: He Held Me Back</a></h4></div></li></ul></div><div class="carousel_tracker" id="story"><div id="boxholder"><div class="indicator indicator2" id="box1"></div><div class="indicator" id="box2"></div><div class="indicator" id="box3"></div><div class="indicator" id="box4"></div></div><div id="arrow-left"><img src="/images/arrow-left.png"></div><div id="arrow-right"><img src="/images/arr